This home features a spacious floor plan, family den, upgraded floors and newer installed A/C unit, Solar Panels and Hurricane proof windows/ doors.  Private backyard and room for a pool.  Enjoy walks to the park and playground, just steps away.   Neighborhood is family oriented.  A definite must-see!
